<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2006-11-30</DATELINE><TITLE>Solid Phase Synthesis of Dual Labeled Peptides: Development of Cell Permeable Calpain Specific Substrates</TITLE><BODY>A step-by-step evaluation of dual-labeled FRET substrates for the protease calpain is reported. The study led to cell permeable selections, with optimized specificity and effectiveness for the target enzyme, and improved stability to non-specific degrading enzymes.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>